Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Pork barrel politics
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3xl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Nov 1979
President Carter uses presidential patronage to counter Kennedy's challenge for leadership. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less